(281, 13, 'exposure', 'medium', 'Type Juggling Risk — Loose Comparison (==) With User Input', 'PHP\'s loose comparison (==) with user input can lead to authentication bypass. E.g., \"0\" == false == null == \"\" == \"0abc\" in PHP\'s loose type system. Attackers can exploit this to bypass authentication or access controls.', 'text-humanizer/admin/thp-admin.php', 'if(isset($_POST[\'action\']) && $_POST[\'action\'] == \'thp_addsettings\' ){', 'text-humanizer/admin/thp-admin.php:188', 'Always use strict comparison (===) when comparing user input. Be especially careful with hash_equals(), in_array (strict mode), and authentication checks.', '2026-03-20 05:50:50'),
(282, 13, 'exposure', 'medium', 'Type Juggling Risk — Loose Comparison (==) With User Input', 'PHP\'s loose comparison (==) with user input can lead to authentication bypass. E.g., \"0\" == false == null == \"\" == \"0abc\" in PHP\'s loose type system. Attackers can exploit this to bypass authentication or access controls.', 'text-humanizer/admin/thp-admin.php', 'if(isset($_POST[\'upType\']) && $_POST[\'upType\']==\"Update\"){', 'text-humanizer/admin/thp-admin.php:201', 'Always use strict comparison (===) when comparing user input. Be especially careful with hash_equals(), in_array (strict mode), and authentication checks.', '2026-03-20 05:50:50'),
