(667, 39, '', 'high', 'Clickjacking — Page Can Be Embedded in External iframes', 'This page is missing both X-Frame-Options and CSP frame-ancestors protection. Attackers can embed this page inside an invisible or transparent iframe on a malicious website and trick users into clicking buttons or links without realising it (UI redress attack). Common targets: account deletion, money transfer, settings changes, one-click purchase buttons.', 'https://hybridai.co.in', NULL, 'X-Frame-Options: not set | CSP frame-ancestors: not found', 'Add to all responses:\nX-Frame-Options: DENY\nContent-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors \'none\';\n\nApache .htaccess:\nHeader always set X-Frame-Options \"DENY\"\nHeader always set Content-Security-Policy \"frame-ancestors \'none\'\"\n\nNginx:\nadd_header X-Frame-Options \"DENY\" always;\nadd_header Content-Security-Policy \"frame-ancestors \'none\'\" always;', '2026-04-01 07:23:43'),
(668, 39, 'authentication', 'high', 'Privileged Endpoint Accessible While Authenticated: /dashboard', 'The endpoint /dashboard returned HTTP 200 with your authenticated session. If this endpoint grants more privileges than expected (admin panel, debug interface, user listing, API config), it represents a privilege escalation or broken access control vulnerability. Attackers who compromise any user account can potentially access admin functionality.', 'https://hybridai.co.in/dashboard', NULL, 'HTTP 200 · Body length: 1545 chars', 'Implement role-based access control (RBAC) on ALL admin/privileged routes:\n\n// CI4 example:\nif (!session()->get(\'is_admin\')) {\n    return redirect()->to(\'/\')->with(\'error\', \'Access denied\');\n}\n\n// Middleware approach (recommended):\n// Register admin middleware that checks role before every admin controller\n// Log all access attempts to sensitive endpoints\n// Implement IP allowlisting for admin panels', '2026-04-01 07:23:48');
