hp.ini to restrict file access to specific directories\",\"Add to php.ini: disable_functions = exec,shell_exec,system,passthru,popen,proc_open\",\"Configure your web server to send the X-Frame-Options response header on all responses\",\"Configure your web server to send the X-Content-Type-Options response header on all responses\",\"Configure your web server to send the X-XSS-Protection response header on all responses\",\"Configure your web server to send the Strict-Transport-Security response header on all responses\",\"Configure your web server to send the Content-Security-Policy response header on all responses\",\"Configure your web server to send the Referrer-Policy response header on all responses\",\"Remove or obfuscate the Server response header to prevent version fingerprinting\",\"Change permissions immediately: chmod 755 G:\\/xmp\\/htdocs\",\"Manually review G:\\/xmp\\/htdocs\\\\eacademy-update\\\\application\\\\config\\\\constants.php \\u2014 it may be a web shell or injected malicious code\",\"Block access to \\/.env via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/.env.local via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/.env.production via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/.git\\/HEAD via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/.git\\/config via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/phpinfo.php via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/info.php via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/test.php via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/config.php via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/.htaccess via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/server-status via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/server-info via web server config or delete the file\",\"Block access to \\/.DS_Store via web server config or delete the file\",\